Welcome to the new and improved JustWatch! We ve been hard at work to make the app faster more reliable and better than ever before! We even threw in a bit of a facelift If you have any feedback you can always reach us via Send Feedback in the settings. No we did not skip basic math we changed the versioning number. We are now using Year.Week instead of just random numbers.

You can exclude genres in the filters. Don t want to see a certain genre no matter what Tap it twice to exclude it. A variety of other bugfixes and improvements
